        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-4">
          What Is Goat Kidding Tracking Software?
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Goat kidding tracking software is a digital system that records every data point about your kids from birth through placement: kidding dates, daily weights, FAMACHA and FEC on the dam, disbudding and tattoo records, and buyer assignments. It replaces paper kidding journals and whelping-app retrofits with a single connected record tied to the doe, buck, pedigree, and waitlist.
